/-
Looking up a key in a filtered list behaves as expected: if the key satisfies the predicate, it's the same as looking up in the original list; otherwise, it's not found.
-/
theorem DagLeanLibrary.SpecialDAG.Graph.lookup_filter_eq_if {α β : Type} [BEq α] [LawfulBEq α]
    (l : List (α × β)) (P : α → Bool) (k : α) :
